IN THE HIGH COURT OF PUNJAB & HARYANA AT CHANDIGARH

CWP No.8343 of 1994

Date of decision:10.07.2012
M/s Garg Trading Company 

 .....Petitioner

Versus
State of Punjab & another

 .....Respondents 

CORAM : HON'BLE MR.JUSTICE G.S.SANDHAWALIA
Present:
None for the petitioner,
Mr.Vijay K.Chaudhary, AAG, Punjab.
*****
G.S.SANDHAWALIA J. (Oral)
.
In the connected case, i.e., CWP No.2086 of 1994, it has been 
submitted that the notification which is under challenge in the present writ 
petition stands superseded by a subsequent notification and therefore, the 
present case has been rendered infructuous.
.
Accordingly, the present writ petition is dismissed as having 
been rendered infructuous. 
.07.2012
 (G.S.SANDHAWALIA)
sailesh
 JUDGE
